    "category": "综合",
    "tags": [
      "前端开发"
    ],
    "updatedAt": "2026-07-01T00:00:00.000Z"
  },
  {
    "id": "fe-faq-046",
    "question": "什么是微任务和宏任务？",
    "answer": "微任务（Promise/MutationObserver）优先级高于宏任务（setTimeout/setInterval）。",
    "category": "综合",
    "tags": [
      "前端开发"
    ],
    "updatedAt": "2026-07-01T00:00:00.000Z"
  },
  {
    "id": "fe-faq-047",
    "question": "什么是虚拟DOM？",
